Review of: Full Day Golden Bridge and Ba Na Hills Small Group Tour
macie b
Vietnam's Fairytale Escape: A Daytrip to Ba Na Hills
Ba Na Hills felt like stepping into a storybook with Jun as our friendly tour guide! The cable car ride was through misty mountains. Jun told us cool things about Vietnam and made us laugh with his funny stories. It was like walking through a giant painting, all beautiful greens and blues with the gold bridge shining. We even rode a crazy rollercoaster! If you want a day filled with fun, flowers, and mountain magic, Ba Na Hills is the place to be! Just make sure to bring your camera for all the amazing things to see.
Review of: Da Nang: Ba Na Hills and Golden Bridge Tour
