mahoo
Awesome experience, perfectly organized
This was a very nice experience. Recommend it to everyone who likes to get the best views and experience of the Hai Van Pass. We booked the tour to ride on the back of one of their professional and very friendly drivers. Everything was organized perfectly from photo stops (plenty of them!) along the route to transferring our backpacks to Hoi An. We always felt safe and got a lot of information along the way. Thanks again for this great day!
